@0 = ~Uh? Hey, you! Are you trying to get into my pocket?~
@1 = ~\[Intelligence\] - I am shocked by the groundlessness of your accusations. I have been anywhere but near you, and I have a whole group of witnesses who will confirm this.~
@2 = ~\[Wisdom\] - Use your head before making such unfounded statements. I was in a hurry and probably hit you as I was passing by. But no one was hurt.~
@3 = ~\[Charisma\] - I assure you, I didn't do it. But I did see a shrouded silhouette walking by. Could that be the real culprit?~
@4 = ~\[Lore\] - On the contrary. I was fascinated by this thing that fell out of your pocket and just wanted to take a closer look at it before returning it to you.~
@5 = ~\[Reputation\] - Hmm, I'll kindly remind you that you're talking to an honorable citizen. Your wallet was dangling from your belt and about to fall. I just wanted to correct him and warn you.~
@6 = ~\[Reputation\] - Maybe you shouldn't make me angry, huh? Shut your mouth and get out of here while you still can.~
@7 = ~(Try to run away.)~
@8 = ~What insolence! Once again, you're trying to steal from me.~
@9 = ~This is the last straw! I won't be robbed by the likes of you!~
@10 = ~Hmm... This time you'll get off with just a warning. This time...~
@11 = ~But from now on, I'll be watching you more closely!~
@12 = ~Bah! I'll close my eyes this time, but don't try it again!~
@13 = ~Great! But remember well, this is your last warning!~
@14 = ~Run wherever you want, thief! But this dirty theft will soon be known!~
@15 = ~This is it! No more apologies!~
@16 = ~This time I will report this brazen robbery attempt! Now get out of my sight!~
@17 = ~Once again, eh, thief? You can't have it! These pathetic attempts at thievery must be stopped.~
